    {
      "id": "FqpdRaPnnlo62J2KmrSGv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1574.1076491820077,
      "y": 4537.765269819357,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c0036",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2031561002,
      "version": 246,
      "versionNonce": 664531212,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782662180333,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "width": 819.3044656676774,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "A Dec is terminal — it admits no successor — yet it is still seal-advancing:\nit carries previousSeal and folds its content run (Ixn s=1, s=2) into\nfolded.canonical. A Dec never carries folded.forks[]: a {Dec, content} race\nresolves by tier-rank (the Dec is the single privileged branch), not a repair.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A Dec is terminal — it admits no successor — yet it is still seal-advancing:\nit carries previousSeal and folds its content run (Ixn s=1, s=2) into\nfolded.canonical. A Dec never carries folded.forks[]: a {Dec, content} race\nresolves by tier-rank (the Dec is the single privileged branch), not a repair.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
