    {
      "angle": 0,
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "seed": 376807116,
      "version": 250,
      "versionNonce": 83481524,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782572683546,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "c021",
      "type": "text",
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "id": "mpd2-106",
      "x": 4799.765625,
      "y": 4600.546875,
      "width": 1358,
      "height": 125,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "setup: two authors A and B. each runs one SEL (owner = their IEL; the SEL Icp's data = V0.said roots it in the constitution V0).\nan edit is a SEL Ixn whose manifest.content names a version SAD; versions chain via ancestors[] (in the SAD) into a multi-parent DAG.\nV0 forks to vA1 and vB1; vM is a multi-parent merge of vA2 + vB1; vA3 and vB2 are two competing tips (presented, never auto-picked;\ntag = canonical, app-level). owner-rooted: a version is valid iff its SEL.owner is in V0.authors[]. readPolicy is fixed at V0 and rides\nevery version. unpictured: the author KELs and full IEL chains (an IEL Ixn anchors every SEL event; only the issuance anchor is drawn).",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "setup: two authors A and B. each runs one SEL (owner = their IEL; the SEL Icp's data = V0.said roots it in the constitution V0).\nan edit is a SEL Ixn whose manifest.content names a version SAD; versions chain via ancestors[] (in the SAD) into a multi-parent DAG.\nV0 forks to vA1 and vB1; vM is a multi-parent merge of vA2 + vB1; vA3 and vB2 are two competing tips (presented, never auto-picked;\ntag = canonical, app-level). owner-rooted: a version is valid iff its SEL.owner is in V0.authors[]. readPolicy is fixed at V0 and rides\nevery version. unpictured: the author KELs and full IEL chains (an IEL Ixn anchors every SEL event; only the issuance anchor is drawn).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
